data.description: This spacious 3 bed 2 bath home located on a little over an acre is ideal country living but not too far from downtown. This home has a living room with a warm wood burning stove, a huge family room, kitchen has lots of storage, updated bathrooms, double pane windows and recent upgraded HVAC system. Shared well with individual pump on the property, metal roof, 2 car garage and circular driveway for easy access. Plenty of room to park your RV, boat or recreational vehicles.
